metadata.name: Wermies Hidden
metadata.description: Wermies are a collection of 10,000 hand drawn and randomly generated NFTs. This is the first collection produced by the Poly Cartel's very own Gergsy. This collection has over two billion (2,000,000,000) possible combinations. Stay tuned on our socials and discord for updates as to when Wermies NFTs will be revealed.
